@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_eeuigp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.sin((wp.abs(v1 + 0.66) + wp.cos(v0 + 0.59)))
    tmp = (wp.exp((v1 + 0.96 * tmp + 0.58)) + wp.abs((v0 + 0.47 - v0 + 0.31)))
    v1 = v2
    v2 = v1
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.sin(wp.cos(v2 + 0.75)))
    v0 = (wp.sin((tmp + 0.41 - v0 + 0.88)) - wp.sin(wp.exp(v2 + 0.01)))
    data[tid] = v0
